OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSouth and
OL,6,Fwest cloudy at first with patchy rain,
OL,7,Fotherwise a dry evening with some late
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Largely clear through
OL,9,Fearly hours but becoming cloudy with
OL,10,Fsome rain later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, heaviest and most
OL,14,Fpersistent across western parts
OL,15,Fthrough the afternoon. The rain turns
OL,16,Fmore showery later with a risk of
OL,17,Fthunder.
